Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay right there, kitty! Don't move an inch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That dream brought back memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}from when I was in fifth grade, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On my way home from school, I found a kitten stuck in a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened next?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Yui? Got a date with Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why does he always tease me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He knows I've never been interested in romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.63,0:01:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boys are wild, heartless, and shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They've caused me nothing but trouble in my time as a class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuuki-kun's no exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}never fall in love.
