Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Kotegawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yuuki-kun? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way home from \N helping my dad with his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been having trouble \N meeting his deadlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't tell him I was going to a pet shop to look at kittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the youth skunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Run took it to school the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We should probably catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't want it to get excited and start releasing gas again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This wouldn't have happened if you hadn't approached it with a scary face!{tlc: I don't really like "a scary face at it" but idk. alt> if you hadn't approached it with such a scary face!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what was I supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! We have to catch it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Our clothes and shoes are too big! They'll slow us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did you look?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! I didn't! I-I didn't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not lying, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not! Th-The s-skunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Peke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, we can get Peke to shrink our clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange. I feel like \NI've seen you before, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, this and that happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that explains everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a crêpe for you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Nana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it just me or...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}does Mea-san look kind of gloomy today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can a Sunday feel this empty without Rito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he still busy helping with Father's manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, just listen to me! I'm talking about his dad like he's my father-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're not related like that...{\i0} yet{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you grinning about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a return skunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My chest's as flat as a board now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yami-san, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Rito-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Our skunk ran out when Ren opened the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! We're looking for it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll search over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness. How could Run-san keep such a dangerous creature as a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She said it'd be irresponsible of her \Nto just send it off to space,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so she read up on how to take care of it and kept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Run has her kind moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're taking her side?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know her cell phone number too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your number too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I explained to you already that I never intend to do anything shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Could've fooled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know. You're not that kind of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he was just a bit different, \Nthen back on that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kotegawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have some big boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're only this big because you're always being so shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I'm to blame?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I guess I'd better take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promise me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promise me you won't do shameless things to anyone but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I nuts? That looks like I{\i0} wanted {\i1}things to go in that direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! Let's catch it before it gets away again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I refuse to admit that a guy like him is my first love!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's out of gas! This is our chance to catch it! It's now or never!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't go up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki-kun, you be careful too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good at this kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:08:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should we care?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always acting like a know-it-all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Find a way to get it down yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go play some games at my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I got my parents to buy me some new stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}F-Fine! Now that it's come to this,\N I'll do whatever it takes to help that cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna be okay, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good at this kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never seen that boy before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha! Don't worry, you're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you did it, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's got a collar, so it must've run away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I saw a poster over there.
