Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's the same cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay! I'll check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't think there were boys like him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those siblings were...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yuuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me one, Yuuki Rito.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Rito-kun, girls!
