Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving it up would make me sad, but I guess it's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever want to see it, just let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks!
