Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.33,0:22:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let things get any more out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.75,0:23:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo, I've awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your harem plan is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.89,0:23:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,With Lala's inventions and your plants,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do whatever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.08,0:23:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it! I'll become a harem demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.07,0:23:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't have a harem as you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Smell this sage flower and return to your senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.52,0:23:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to your normal, sincere self.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kind and you respect girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what allows you to—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.41,0:23:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He passed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.71,0:23:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He must've seen something quite intense during his rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.05,0:24:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be in such a rush to become a womanizer, Rito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.53,0:24:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lead you down the right path, little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.92,0:24:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I overreacted earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.27,0:24:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But only because you were being so shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be careful not to—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.26,0:24:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing! I saw nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.92,0:24:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
